            "type": "text",
            "text": "Monitor latency and throughput using built-in metrics. For Qwen Image Edit Plus, batch requests to reduce overhead and leverage GPU acceleration. Implement caching for frequent edits to minimize model reloads. Compare with Nano Banana's lower latency but limited edit capabilities—optimize by offloading simple tasks to Nano Banana while reserving Qwen Image Edit Plus for complex operations."
